{"type":"message","id":"a8e284ef","parentId":"7289e5ca","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:04:03.678Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session in the last 5 minutes is this cron job itself. The cron job triggered this check, and the messages show only the cron job's own messages (not user messages). There's no active user conversation. \n\nWait - let me think about this more carefully. The `sessions_list` shows sessions that have been active in the last 5 minutes. The only session shown is the cron session itself (`agent:main:cron:3709e1d2...`). The `messages` array shows the cron job's own internal messages (the tool call to sessions_list). This is not a user conversation.\n\nSo there's no active user conversation. I should perform the self-learning task.\n\nLet me search for the latest news on:\n1. 企业数字化转型 (Enterprise Digital Transformation)\n2. 智能安防 (Smart Security)\n3. 网络系统集成 (Network System Integration)\n4. IT运维服务 (IT Operations Services)\n\nI should use the web search skill to find this information.","thinkingSignature":"915f3077dd111388e5d59997ca9bf62a6782c2434eb5b1a60066968a7d092bd4"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前无用户活跃对话（仅cron自身会话），执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w7uz7lts8cbw_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":876,"output":260,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45117,"cost":{"input":0.0002628,"output":0.000312,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018942299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775066636522}}
{"type":"message","id":"ea683148","parentId":"a8e284ef","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:04:03.687Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_w7uz7lts8cbw_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775066643683}}
