{"type":"message","id":"d9eb30e7","parentId":"1e4915ac","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:05:46.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. I've successfully:\n1. Checked sessions - found no active user conversation (only the cron job itself)\n2. Performed 5 parallel web searches on relevant topics\n3. Compiled the learning notes with 5 key insights and 3 actionable recommendations\n4. Saved to the designated file\n\nLet me provide a brief summary.","thinkingSignature":"9b28749d7187911a5132f8ecce6d764c81f1bba7b06b0c5eaf8ee94e29f3953a"},{"type":"text","text":"**自主学习完成 ✅**\n\n检测到无活跃用户对话，已执行空闲时段自主学习。整理了5条关键洞察，保存至 `memory/学习笔记.md`：\n\n| # | 主题 | 核心要点 |\n|---|------|----------|\n| 1 | AI安防大模型落地 | 边缘AI芯片渗透率超75%，\"云-边-端\"架构成为主流 |\n| 2 | 安防场景化深耕 | 全球市场规模3500亿美元，中国占30%，场景方案替代通用产品 |\n| 3 | AIOps运维革命 | \"人头租赁\"模式面临淘汰，向\"效果付费+智能预测\"转型 |\n| 4 | 安全内生成核心竞争力 | 零信任从可选变强制，网络集成商安全能力成差异化关键 |\n| 5 | 多智能体协作兴起 | Gartner将MAS列为2026年十大战略技术趋势之一 |\n\n**3条核心行动建议**：① 加速AIOps运维能力建设；② 安防方案向AI视觉+边缘计算升级；③ 网络集成项目嵌入安全能力。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6811,"output":292,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51084,"cost":{"input":0.0020433,"output":0.0003504,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00371313}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775066737991}}
